column5: Since there were no steelhead involved, or salmonoids for that matter.. We put in about 5 hours with some missed hits and spotted some salmon. All I caught personally is a kingfisher which decided to fly into my line. Greensot hooked into a monster clam and Sleded managed big (and only) fish of the day with a channel cat on a roe bag. What a night!!!
hey,at least you didn't get skunked
or you could have stayed home and cut the grass..... naw no fishis better than that.   Art
